comment._content: Accompanying note: "Lincoln High's basketball team won the state championship and went to the second round of the National tournament at Nashville, Tenn., last year. This is the 1956-57 squad. Front row, left to right: Coach Nick Nims, Issac Henderson, Garrett Eummer, Raymond Dickey, William Barnes, Tyrome Martine, Robert Lynn, Hillard Jenkins. Back row: Riley Lander, Raleigh Jugger, Melvin Caswell, Sidney Green, Willie Price, Leroy Fields, Donald Williams, John Jefferson."
comment.authorname: State Library and Archives of Florida
